Dal 2001 al 2002 fu in vendita la versione limitata "Tenni", in 150 esemplari, con frizione monodisco, dedicata al famoso pilota degli anni '30.
Dal 2003 al 2005 fu in vendita la versione "Rosso Corsa", e dal 2004 al 2005 la versione "Nero Corsa", con sospensioni Öhlins e altri particolari pregiati.

notes.en:
In 2003 the engine was made Euro 3 compliant with:
EFI Marelli 15RC;
Compression ratio increased to 9.8:1;
Max rpm increased to 8200 (same power);
Fuel tank reduced by 2 liters (approx. 2 quarts);
43mm front fork.
From 2001 to 2002 the "Tenni" limited edition was sold, in memory of the famous racing rider of the thirties, in only 150 models. It has a single plate clutch.
From 2003 to 2005 the "Rosso Corsa" version was sold, and from 2004 to 2005 the "Nero Corsa" version was sold, both with Öhlins suspensions and other valuable components.

